    <div class="message" id="message">
      üéÇ <b>Happy Birthday, my love!</b> üéÇ<br><br>
      Today is all about celebrating <b>YOU</b> a truly special person in my life,with the kindest heart and the brightest smile.  
      I just want you to know how much I love you, and how proud I am of everything you are and all that you‚Äôre becoming. üíï  
